name: Kasadya
description:
The visuals gets its cues from karaoke aesthetics along with Christmas decorations. 

The character is inspired by my yearly tradition of making callos for the family Noche buena.  

The audio is a psychedelic remix (with permission) from DJ Jansnow's Budots version of "Kasadya Ning Taknaa" the classic Cebuano Christmas song that is the basis for the classic "Ang Pakso ay Sumapit."
